              <li>Fall</li>
              <li>Prerequisites: PSYC 213 and PSYC 311, and one of PSYC 305 OR BIOL 373, or permission of instructor.</li>
              <li>Restrictions: Open only to Psychology,  Cognitive Science and Neuroscience students.  Not open to students who have taken PSYC 365.</li>
            </ul>
      </div>

